        <img src="http://setmoney.blob.core.windows.net/newsimages/2015/12/02/393954-SOURCE.jpg" />
        <figcaption>▲Instant Article與手機的深度整合，體驗起來很不一樣。（圖／Facebook）</figcaption>
      </figure>
